gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a62866f3654e702359e66ce33349beea4da89e","tid":2194996,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:39:24.000Z","msg":"石<br />\n腳"},{"pid":"9297ff5bc3ec897b3a4fa817927faa9a85a0479c","tid":2194996,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"環時：澳洲情報人員突擊搜查中國駐澳記者住所"},{"pid":"7bd7e5041995cf87f01071a5bbef09b4a2987212","tid":2194996,"uid":254788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"呢啲叫對等行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f4cf893374c09758b8ec177e28659d5f0d9583","tid":2194996,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:49:31.000Z","msg":"毛澤東後首度無澳媒駐中記者 外記協會斥北京令人恐懼<br />\n<br />\n澳洲媒體兩名駐中記者被迫「逃離」中國，出現自毛澤東年代以來（1970年代中期後），首度沒有任何獲官方認證的澳媒記者可直接報導中國新聞的局面，立下令人擔憂的先例。事實上，習近平上台後，外國記者要報導中國新聞越來越難，在中國境內受到越來越多限制，很少中國民眾或學者願意冒險接受外媒訪問。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200909/7KWYTXZE6VBWNK6WTBRQ7IPB3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200909%2F7KWYTXZE6VBWNK6WTBRQ7IPB3E%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=2e177dca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200909%2F7KWYTXZE6VBWNK6WTBRQ7IPB3E%2F&h=64c66f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200909/7KWYTXZE6VBWNK6WTBRQ7IPB3E/</a>"},{"pid":"a0cef6053487635672025fd590cbed4e513572d3","tid":2194996,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:52:15.000Z","msg":"赤納粹滲透全世界"},{"pid":"34a5cb52880b26ac62b0e274fa0653253b17258e","tid":2194996,"uid":364767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"成龍說：中國人是要管的<br />\n左派傳媒更加要管，否則日日妖言惑眾<br />\n報道埋啲假新聞，外交部係咁，何況普通傳媒記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vdo-go.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/italy-1-696x392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvdo-go.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2Fitaly-1-696x392.jpg&h=eda7ca0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"595b2275d99c18cf6203af57a3a5b567c5ee50ff","tid":2194996,"uid":172793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b735761dd52c389a7b97467b7fd92568a582433","tid":2194996,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>都係學支那啫 大家咁話</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a7f40b57dd2e37f06c32cfd7c7606c107ad23c03","tid":2194996,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T02:34:10.000Z","msg":"中國媒體記者沒有一個蘑菇"},{"pid":"5e0067016074373fef31fd014c0cdce248e91c1e","tid":2194996,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越來越精彩"},{"pid":"ed9435f581a1e3a23c58ee8cf4a247df5fa29cb7","tid":2194996,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2237566b799eedcd4f4679331fb8d6be25d4725c","tid":2194996,"uid":323373,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T01:26:00.000Z","msg":"以其人之道還自其人之身  <strong><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"正解"}]}